      "extraction_notes": "Interpreted 'पञ्चांशकाः प्रोक्तं त्रिकोणम्' (the fifth house is said to be a trine) as indicating temporary friendship. Trines (5th and 9th houses) are generally considered auspicious and friendly positions in Vedic astrology, aligning with standard temporary relationship rules where the 5th house indicates friendship."
    },
