        "calculation": "If the planet is retrograde, the standard addition/deduction process for Chaalana (time difference adjustment based on Ishta Kaala vs. Mishra Kaala) is reversed. Specifically, if Ishta Kaala is before Mishra Kaala, add Chaalana; if Ishta Kaala is after Mishra Kaala, deduct Chaalana.",
