        "calculation": "Identify the planet's exaltation sign and debilitation sign. A planet gets full strength in its exaltation sign. Its strength diminishes gradually as it moves from its exaltation sign towards its debilitation sign, becoming nil in its debilitation sign. The strength in between is considered proportional.",
