      "extraction_notes": "Rule derived from the statement 'A planet gets full strength in his exaltation sign. As he rises from this sign and progresses towards his debilitation sign, his strength begins to diminish gradually till at length it becomes nil when he enters in his debilitation sign. Therefore, the strength of the planet in between his exaltation and debilitation signs may be considered in proportion.'"
