      "expert_verified": false,
      "extraction_notes": "This rule is derived from 'तथा पश्यन्ति पार्श्वभे' (And they aspect, excluding the adjacent ones), establishing a general exception for all Rashi Drishti rules: signs do not aspect their immediately adjacent signs (2nd and 12th from themselves). This is a foundational principle for Rashi Drishti."
