      "extraction_notes": "This rule describes a fundamental principle for resolving contradictions arising from a single planet's dual lordship. It states that if a planet rules two houses whose indications are conflicting and of equal strength, both indications are nullified or destroyed. This implies a prior step of strength assessment for the planet's ability to deliver results from each house."
