        "condition": "When determining the motional strength (Chesta Bala) of Mars, its Chesta Kendra must be calculated correctly.",
        "calculation": "Chesta Kendra for Mars is calculated as: ((Mars's Mean Longitude + Mars's True Longitude) / 2) - Mars's Manda Ucca (Apogee). If the resulting value is greater than 6 signs (180 degrees), it must be subtracted from 12 signs (360 degrees) to obtain the final Chesta Kendra.",
