        "calculation": "1. Identify natural malefics (Saturn, Mars, Rahu, Ketu, waning Moon). 2. Identify the lords of the 9th and 10th houses for the specific Lagna. 3. Exclude any natural malefic that is also a 9th or 10th house lord. 4. Check if any of the remaining malefics are situated in the Ascendant (Lagna). 5. Identify Maraka planets (typically lords of the 2nd and 7th houses, and planets associated with them). 6. Determine if the malefic in Lagna (from step 4) is in conjunction with or aspected by any identified Maraka planet.",
