        "calculation": "Determine the planet's degree within its sign (0-30). If the sign is odd, apply the following ranges: 0-6 degrees (Baala/infant), 6-12 degrees (Kumara/youthful), 12-18 degrees (Yuva/adolescent), 18-24 degrees (Vridha/advanced), 24-30 degrees (Mrita/deceased). If the sign is even, reverse the order: 0-6 degrees (Mrita/deceased), 6-12 degrees (Vridha/advanced), 12-18 degrees (Yuva/adolescent), 18-24 degrees (Kumara/youthful), 24-30 degrees (Baala/infant). Each avastha spans 6 degrees.",
